sql:
SELECT MAX(accuracy) 
FROM evaluation_metrics 
WHERE dataset_id = (SELECT dataset_id FROM datasets WHERE dataset_name = 'my_dataset');

external_knowledge:
- 'Golden touch' refers to the best or most skilled models; 
- 'The Foundation' refers to the dataset with dataset_id = 2; 
- 'Exceptional neural network prowess' refers to models with model_type = 'Neural Network' and high accuracy; 
- 'Nearing perfection' refers to accuracy > 0.85; 
- 'Crème de la crème' refers to the top 10 models with the highest F-scores for class 1.

